<div class="body">
  <div class="home">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="left-side">
        <h1><strong>RIDE TO ROMANCE,<br></strong> NATURALLY</h1>
        <p>Discover the perfect date itinerary! Say goodbye to the hassle of planning, and let us guide you through the best subway stations for a memorable experience. </p>
        <p>Start your journey to a unforgettable date today!</p>
        <div class="call-to-action">
          <%= link_to "Explore now", itineraries_path, class: "btn-blue" %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="right-side">
        <%= image_tag "Date", class: "header-img" %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="home-search">
      <%= render "shared/home_search" %>
    </div>

    <div class="app-features">
      <h2>What We Provide</h2>
      <h1>BRINGING YOU THE BEST DATE EXPERIENCES!</h1>
      <div class="features-card">
        <div class="first-card">
          <%= image_tag "road_icon" , class: "card-img" %>
          <h3>Optimize Your Date</h3>
          <p>Perfect for your next dates and saving time on planning it!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="second-card">
          <%= image_tag "love_paperplane_icon" , class: "card-img" %>
          <h3>Share Your Experiences</h3>
          <p>Youâ€™ll probably help create a new couple, who knows?</p>
        </div>
        <div class="third-card">
          <%= image_tag "review_icon" , class: "card-img" %>
          <h3>Leave A Review</h3>
          <p>Did you love your date or was it a disaster? Help people to find the best itinerary for their date.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="top-itineraries">
      <div class="title">
        <h1>FIND YOUR PERFECT DATE ITINERARY</h1>
        <p>Discover romantic destinations through subway station - with insider tips and recommendations from our community. <span>So what's your next date?</span></p>
      </div>
      <%= render "shared/top_itinerary_card" %>
      <div class="text-btn">
        <p>Have a unique date idea? <br> Share it with others and inspire their next adventure.</p>
        <%= link_to "Write your own itinerary", new_itinerary_path, class: "btn-pink-sabrina" %>
      </div>
  </div>

  <div class="end-page">
    <div class="left-side">
      <h2>Time To PLan It</h2>
      <h1>READY FOR AN UNFORGETTABLE DATE?</h1>
      <div class="end-page-btn">
        <%= link_to "Start dating", itineraries_path, class: "btn-blue" %>
        <%= link_to "Sign up", user_session_path, class: "btn-pink-bordered" %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="right-side">
      <%= image_tag "end-page-image", class: "side-img" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
